      static OFPort OFPort.FLOOD

      static OFPort OFPort.NO_MASK 
      static OFPort OFPort.NORMAL
      Process with normal L2/L3 switching.
      static OFPort OFPort.TABLE
      Submit the packet to the first flow table NB: This destination port can only be used in packet-out messages.
      static OFPort OFPort.ZERO
      the wildcarded default for OpenFlow 1.0 (value: 0).
